+## [0.4.9] - 2026-05-19
+
+- Repaired a malformed compiled `out/acpClient.js` header that had leaked method-body code into the top-level CommonJS wrapper and prevented the extension from activating with a top-level `await` parse error.
+- Kept the ACP file-system capability hotfix (`readTextFile` / `writeTextFile`) intact while restoring the generated module prologue required by the installed extension package.
+
 ## [0.4.8] - 2026-05-19
 
 - Added the Command Palette action `ACP: Import Auggie manual commands`, which runs `auggie command help`, parses the custom-command catalog, and stores the results in `acpClient.agents.auggie.manualCommands` in user settings.
